OL,3,CNext government should consider
OL,4,Cbanning phones for under-16s, report
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThe next government should consider a
OL,8,Fstatutory ban on mobile phones in
OL,9,Fschools and a total ban on phones for
OL,10,Funder-16s, a report from MPs says.
OL,12,FThe House of Commons Education
OL,13,FCommittee said tougher guidance on
OL,14,Fmobile phones in schools and how to
OL,15,Fmanage children's screen time at home
OL,16,Fis needed to better protect young
OL,17,Fpeople.
