OL,3,CNext government should consider
OL,4,Cbanning phones for under-16s, report
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FIt argued that screen time was harmful
OL,8,Fto children's mental and physical
OL,9,Fhealth, and both schools and parents
OL,10,Fneeded clear guidance from the
OL,11,FGovernment on the issue.
OL,13,FEarlier this year, the Department for
OL,14,FEducation issued guidance, which is
OL,15,Fnon-statutory, instructing
OL,16,Fheadteachers on how to ban the use of
OL,17,Fphones not only during lessons but
OL,18,Fduring break and lunch periods as
OL,19,Fwell, and suggesting that staff could
OL,20,Fsearch pupils and their bags for
OL,21,Fmobile phones if necessary.
