OL,3,CNext government should consider
OL,4,Cbanning phones for under-16s, report
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FIt said there had been a 52% increase
OL,8,Fin children's screen time between 2020
OL,9,Fand 2022, with a quarter said to be
OL,10,Fusing their devices in an addictive
OL,11,Fmanner.
OL,13,FThe report said it had found that for
OL,14,Fsome, screen time was beginning at as
OL,15,Fearly as six months of age, with one
OL,16,Fin five children aged between three
OL,17,Fand four now having their own mobile
OL,18,Fphone, with almost all children now
OL,19,Fhaving one by the time they were 12.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/11
