OL,3,CNext government should consider
OL,4,Cbanning phones for under-16s, report
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FMPs on the committee said that while
OL,8,Fthe Online Safety Act will play a role
OL,9,Fin keeping children safe from online
OL,10,Fharms, full protection will not come
OL,11,Funtil the Act is fully implemented in
OL,12,F2026.
OL,14,FCommittee chairman Robin Walker said:
OL,15,F"Excessive screen and smartphone use
OL,16,Fhas a clear negative impact on the
OL,17,Fmental and physical wellbeing of
OL,18,Fchildren and young people.
