OL,3,CNext government should consider
OL,4,Cbanning phones for under-16s, report
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"Whilst there can be some benefits
OL,8,Ffrom the online world and sharing
OL,9,Finformation or interests with their
OL,10,Fpeers, ready, unsupervised and
OL,11,Funrestricted access to the internet
OL,12,Fleaves children vulnerable, exposing
OL,13,Fthem to a world they are not equipped
OL,14,Ffor. Their safeguarding and protection
OL,15,Fmust be our priority."
