OL,3,CNext government should consider
OL,4,Cbanning phones for under-16s, report
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FMr Russell, who set up and is now
OL,8,Fchairman of the Molly Rose Foundation
OL,9,Fsuicide prevention charity, said: "The
OL,10,Fnext government must follow the
OL,11,Fevidence and deliver stronger
OL,12,Fregulation, not policies that would be
OL,13,Fslower to implement and deliver worse
OL,14,Foutcomes.
OL,16,F"The quickest and most effective route
OL,17,Fto protect children's online safety
OL,18,Fand wellbeing is to strengthen the
OL,19,FOnline Safety Act in the next
OL,20,Fparliament and we call on all parties
OL,21,Fto commit to this in their manifestos."
